{"tid":1038901,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港修引渡條例如矮化我主權　陸委會：不會接受","createTime":"2019-02-27T04:52:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-05T02:38:35.000Z","uid":47714,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"03569be297a63e1e02e1da84f4af1d0eed79f0ee","tid":1038901,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T04:52:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/2705341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F2705341&d=zkxYWYOkbsQg7WdKzXEy6ZKGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=bfa4f8da\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F2705341&h=50851ce0\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/2705341</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpY8votz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpY8votz.jpg&h=43a078ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n時代力量黨團主任陳惠敏（左）、立委徐永明（中）今召開香港修改「引渡中國條例」、台人赴港人身安全陷危機記者會，要求法務部及陸委會表態，陸委會黃廷輝（右）出席說明。（記者簡榮豐攝）<br />\n<br />\n〔記者謝君臨／台北報導〕針對香港政府討論修法，可以跟沒有簽訂引渡協議的地方進行個案合作，引發台灣人赴港恐成為李明哲第二，遭遣送中國疑慮；對此，立法院時代力量黨團總召徐永明呼籲，政府及各政黨都應積極表態，反對矮化台灣主權的作法；陸委會也強調，我國政府不會接受任何消滅國家主權的作法。<br />\n<br />\n香港政府修法肇因於港女來台遭殺害棄屍案，由於台港之間沒有引渡協議，導致兇嫌返港後，無法引渡來台接受調查；香港保安局日前建議修改相關條例，將引渡嫌犯的程序，適用於與任何未訂有協定的地方，包括中、澳、台等；對此，香港社運人士黃之鋒提出警告，修法恐讓台人赴港成為李明哲第二。"},{"pid":"9670aba5aadbe73c799a18123b04f490013bdb95","tid":1038901,"uid":192517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T10:59:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cae2c111ba650d00b75f2210254248a78b8ea99a","tid":1038901,"uid":192517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T02:38:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}